###

### 🍱 POST crea un nuovo poke bowl
POST http://localhost:3000/api/pokes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sizeID": 1,
  "elementIDs": [1, 5, 8, 9]  
}

###

### 🧾 POST crea un nuovo ordine
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userID": 1,
  "pokes": [
    { "pokeID": 3, "quantity": 2 },
    { "pokeID": 4, "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "totalPrice": 37.80
}

###

### 🧍‍♂️ GET tutti gli ordini dell’utente 1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders/user/1

###

### 🔍 GET dettagli di un ordine specifico (es. ID = 2)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders/2
